    "Therefore, by constructing a new graph from the original heterogeneous graph with the static meta-structure, we can perform community search through meta-path on the new graph.",
    "This process is equivalent to searching through meta-structures, a claim that we will prove later.",
    "Based on this, we design an efficient algorithm for performing graph reconstruction in batch.Figure 5a displays a simple heterogeneous graph.",
